 Nijisanji Leos Vincent 参加“50公里禁烟马拉松”并在约10小时内完成https://www.moguravr.com/leos-vincent-50km/ノンジャンル人生 Tue, 12 Mar 2024 10:57:13 +0000 VTuberにじさんじレオス・ヴィンセントhttps://www.moguravr.com/?p=247815 <p> VTuber团体“Nijisanji”的成员Leos Vincent因尝试“50公里禁烟马拉松”而成为热门话题。 Leos Vincent很早就公开表示自己是烟民。然而，到 2024 年 […]</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/leos-vincent-50km/">Nijisanji Leos Vincent 参加“50公里无烟马拉松”并在大约 10 小时内完成的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; <p> VTuber团体“ <a href="https://www.nijisanji.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nijisanji</a> ”的成员<a href="https://twitter.com/Leos_Vincent" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Leos Vincent</strong></a>因尝试参加<strong>“50公里禁烟马拉松”而成为热门话题。</strong></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.yboomqvpglz6-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.yboomqvpglz6-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.yboomqvpglz6-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.yboomqvpglz6-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.yboomqvpglz6-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> Leos Vincent很早就公开表示自己是烟民。然而，在2024年生日直播时，他突然宣布要跑“50公里禁烟马拉松”。观众们一头雾水，但为了表达对观众的感谢，Leos宣布他将在演播室以3D直播的方式跑50公里。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.r1d8db7brjg0-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.r1d8db7brjg0-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.r1d8db7brjg0-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.r1d8db7brjg0-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.r1d8db7brjg0-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>马拉松直播将于 3 月 11 日 11:00 开始。她兴奋地跟他打招呼，麦克风都爆裂了，但工作人员似乎很担心她。他夸口说<strong>：“我不在乎今天一切是否结束，这可能是Leos Vincent的退休广播。”</strong>但他也表示，几年前他实际上已经跑过20公里，显示出他的自信。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.gv5e17dty91x-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.gv5e17dty91x-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.gv5e17dty91x-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.gv5e17dty91x-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.gv5e17dty91x-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>马拉松比赛马上开始了。身后有流动的背景图像，里奥先生一边说着轻松的笑话，一边加快了速度。显然，策略是先跑，然后多说话，预计他下半场就不会说话了。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.2oarivt7ndd7-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.2oarivt7ndd7-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.2oarivt7ndd7-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.2oarivt7ndd7-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.2oarivt7ndd7-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> Leos在观众的欢呼声中不断前进。<a href="https://twitter.com/kei_nagao2434" target="_blank" rel="noopener">长尾圭</a>作为嘉宾出现在这里。他们会为该项目的目的而欢呼，但似乎嘉宾实际上有一个唱歌和支持的使命。她演唱的歌曲<strong>是《Runner》，这是一首作为跑步支持歌曲而广为人知的歌曲。</strong> Leos先生和观众们也很兴奋。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.251coglg1hxm-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.251coglg1hxm-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.251coglg1hxm-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.251coglg1hxm-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.251coglg1hxm-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>之后，<a href="https://twitter.com/Levi_E_2434" target="_blank" rel="noopener">利维·埃利法</a>、<a href="https://twitter.com/846kizuQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">沙月</a>、<a href="https://twitter.com/___Dola" target="_blank" rel="noopener">朵拉</a>作为嘉宾登场。尤其是唱歌的VTuber们当然会用《Runner》来支持我们。到目前为止，广播的令人惊奇之处在于，莱奥斯先生在客人到达时与他们进行了深入的交谈。他不只是奔跑，他还展现了他的流光精神。</p><p>每两个小时休息一次，我们稳步行驶了10公里，然后是15公里。此外，一些支持该活动的粉丝似乎也在与直播同时进行。主题标签 X（以前的 Twitter）充满了支持插图，并且兴奋感持续增长。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.uo11ajat9ubx-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.uo11ajat9ubx-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.uo11ajat9ubx-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.uo11ajat9ubx-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.uo11ajat9ubx-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>此外，嘉宾也会陆续出现。<a href="https://twitter.com/saku_sasaki" target="_blank" rel="noopener">佐佐木咲</a>秀太黑模仿，破坏狮子座腹肌不过，我跑得很快，比如在跑4小时的时候跑了23公里。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.j9g2kukc86sq-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.j9g2kukc86sq-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.j9g2kukc86sq-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.j9g2kukc86sq-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.j9g2kukc86sq-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> Leos转了25公里，与客人顺利同行。但到了30公里的时候，你就能感受到长跑的严格性，比如感觉双脚有负担，并逐渐减轻。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.crk5iwnppwh1-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.crk5iwnppwh1-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.crk5iwnppwh1-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.crk5iwnppwh1-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.crk5iwnppwh1-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>狮子座一边继续走得更远，一边呼唤着一位活泼的客人。全程马拉松距离超过了最后冲刺的距离。即使步伐下降，也没有破坏我自己至今的光芒。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.e7av1wsvc5n1-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.e7av1wsvc5n1-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.e7av1wsvc5n1-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.e7av1wsvc5n1-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.e7av1wsvc5n1-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> 50公里多一点。最后，Leos自己也激励自己，比如根据BGM哼唱《Runner》。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.p2k412fws4ed-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.p2k412fws4ed-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.p2k412fws4ed-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.p2k412fws4ed-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/fbbc3ff188c94bea6fef61ab24ad0bb0-kix.p2k412fws4ed-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>最后花了近10个小时才跑完50公里。目标是等待 Mame Nicks 提前从观众中招募的欢迎插画。他说：“下半身没有任何疼痛。”但他也感谢粉丝和工作人员。此外，在马拉松赛后的双播分布中，烟草似乎已被牢固地提升。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【支持凸等待】50km吸烟马拉松耐久度【Leos Vincent】" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/i3ZkPy8WS00?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 2024 年，Leos Vincent 已进入第四个年头，但仍在从事具有挑战性的活动。不要错过您将要分发的分发类型。 </p><div class="mg-mogura-card m-0 mb-2 mb-md-3"><div class="d-flex"><div class="mg-mogura-card-thumb position-relative"><img class="mg-img-cover position-absolute h-100 w-100" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/02/202302151415799000-300x169.jpg"></div><div cla